quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  98,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  98,1,jo log kafir hain ( yani ) ahal kitaab aur mushriq woh ( kufar se ) baz rehne walay nah they jab taq un ke paas khuli Daleel ( nah ) aati
  98,2,( yani ) khuda ke paighambar jo pak ourak parhte hain
  98,3,jin mein ( mustahkam ) ayatain likhi hui hain
  98,4,aur ahal kitaab jo mutafarraq ( o mukhtalif ) hue hain to Daleel wazeh anay ke baad ( hue hain )
  98,5,aur un ko hukum to yahi howa tha ke ikhlaas amal ke sath khuda ki ibadat karen ( aur ) yaksu ho kar aur namaaz parheen aur zakaat den aur yahi sacha deen hai
  98,6,jo log kafir hain ( yani ) ahal kitaab aur mushriq woh dozakh ki aag mein parrin ge ( aur ) hamesha is mein rahen ge. yeh log sab makhlooq se badter hain
  98,7,( aur ) jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay woh tamam khalqat se behtar hain
  98,8,un ka sila un ke perwar-digaar ke haan hamesha rehne ke baagh hain jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain abad al abaad un mein rahen ge. khuda un se khush aur woh is se khush. yeh ( sila ) is ke liye hai jo apne perwar-digaar se darta raha
